<h2 style="color: #007bff;">Unlock Account Instructions</h2>

<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>Your account has been locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign in attempts.</p>

<p>Click the link below to unlock your account:</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px;">
  <%= link_to 'Unlock my account', unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token), style: "display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
</p>